posting_body: ['Sparc at Spring District', '1201 121st Avenue NE, Bellevue, WA, 98005', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 167', 'OR Text', '167', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Live where ideas and interests ignite', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 773 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Be among the first to live in The Spring District in Bellevue, Washington.', 'We are creating a neighborhood that draws people in, sparks both business and personal passions weaving an intellectual tapestry that drives new ideas.', 'Sparc Apartments is the catalyst welcoming you to a new living experience where urban meets suburban.', 'Lease studios, one, two and three bedroom apartments.', 'Not to mention innovative Townhomes and Live work lofts.', 'Live minutes from Downtown Bellevue, Kirkland, Redmond with easy access to I-405 and the Microsoft Campus.', 'Features', '- Patios and balconies in select homes', '- Custom pendant lights in kitchen', '- Full size, stacked washer and dryer', '- Floor-to-ceiling windows in select homes', '- Quartz countertops in kitchen and bathrooms', '- Stainless or black Whirlpool appliances', '- Berber carpet and vinyl plank flooring', '- Electric or gas range', 'Community Amenities', '- 4,500 SF outdoor playground', '- Bicycle storage & repair station', '- Raised garden beds', '- Mini putting green', '- Catering kitchen', '- Rooftop deck', '- Games & TV lounge', '- Well-stocked fitness center', '- Wi-Fi Lounge', '- Event space', '- Early childhood education center', '- Pet washing station', '- Greenhouse', '- Public courtyard', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'pwxM8xhA4']
